
This directory contains the source code of the program. Functions and classes are organized 
into modules, with most of the documentation found in the corresponding header (*.hpp) file.


Compilation instructions
-------------------------------
The program, in its entirety, is compiled using the attached Makefile, i.e. by running:

make


Contents of this directory
-------------------------------

src/
├── README --------------------- This file
├── city.hpp ------------------- A header file where the City data structure is defined
├── main.cpp ------------------- The main program file 
├── Makefile ------------------- A makefile for compiling the program
├── genetics.cpp --------------- A module containing genetics related functions
├── genetics.hpp --------------- The C++ header for the above file
├── individ.cpp ---------------- A module containing the Individ class
├── individ.hpp ---------------- The C++ header for the above file
├── IO.cpp --------------------- A module containing functions for parsing input files
│                                and writing output to both screen and file
├── IO.hpp --------------------- The C++ header for the above file
├── parallel.cpp --------------- A module containing functions related to MPI communication
├── parallel.hpp --------------- The C++ header for the above file
└── random.hpp ----------------- All things related to random number generation 


